# Immutable Models

`ViewModel`, `DrawLine`, `Lines` extend Immutable `Record`. Never mutate in place.

```typescript
// BAD
line.points.push(x);

// GOOD
return this.set("points", this.points.push(x));
```

## Line keys

- Local mode: sequential strings (`"0"`, `"1"`, ...)
- Online mode: Firebase `push()` keys

## Related files

- Canvas/view: `ViewModel.ts` — `move`, `scaleAt`, `rotateAt`
- Drawing/erase: `LineModel.ts` — `getCrossingLine` deletes whole lines on intersection
